<h2>1. Executive Directive</h2>
<p><strong>SkillVector</strong> is a high-velocity competence acquisition engine designed to optimize the "Mean Time to Proficiency" (MTTP) for engineering squads. Unlike passive LMS (Learning Management Systems), SkillVector employs an <strong>Event-Driven Architecture</strong> to enforce active engagement, cryptographic-grade verification, and friction-free knowledge ingestion.</p>

<p><strong>Strategic North Star:</strong> Achieve a <strong>5x reduction in administrative overhead</strong> while guaranteeing <strong>100% compliance auditability</strong> through automated, heartbeat-driven telemetry.</p>

<h2>2. User Matrix & Psychological Profiles</h2>

<h3>2.1 Admin Persona: "The Engineering Director" (Mike)</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Cognitive Model:</strong> "Trust but Verify."</li>
    <li><strong>SLO Requirement:</strong> <strong>&lt; 200ms</strong> Time-to-Insight. Requires aggregated "Traffic Light" telemetry.</li>
</ul>

<h3>2.2 Learner Persona: "The 10x Engineer" (Sarah)</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Cognitive Model:</strong> "Flow State Preservation."</li>
    <li><strong>Requirement:</strong> Context-Attached Memory. Notes must be strictly bound to video time-indices (temporal binding).</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Architectural Stack & Decision Records (ADR)</h2>

<h3>Option 1: No-Code (Airtable)</h3>
<p><strong>Verdict: REJECTED.</strong> Fails to support Custom Event Emitters required for heartbeat logic.</p>

<h3>Option 2: Monolithic MERN</h3>
<p><strong>Verdict: REJECTED.</strong> Violation of "YAGNI" principle. Managing stateful node clusters is unnecessary OpEx.</p>

<h3>Option 3: Distributed Serverless (Supabase + React)</h3>
<p><strong>Verdict: APPROVED (SELECTED).</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Data Consistency:</strong> ACID compliant via Postgres.</li>
    <li><strong>Latency:</strong> O(1) content access via Edge CDN.</li>
    <li><strong>Security:</strong> Zero Trust model via RLS.</li>
</ul>

