<h2>5. Functional Specifications</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>FR-CORE-01 (Heartbeat Protocol):</strong> Client emits signed <code>heartbeat</code> event every 30s.</li>
    <li><strong>FR-CORE-02 (Gatekeeper Logic):</strong> <code>isComplete = (videoProgress > 0.9) && (quizScore > 0.8)</code></li>
    <li><strong>FR-CORE-03 (Temporal Binding):</strong> Notes stored as tuple <code>(userId, moduleId, timestamp, content)</code>.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Non-Functional Requirements (SLOs)</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>P99 Latency:</strong> Dashboard load &lt; 200ms.</li>
    <li><strong>Security:</strong> TLS 1.3 (ChaCha20-Poly1305), AES-256 GCM at rest.</li>
</ul>

